text: It's day 1 of the lockdown and already a car break down reveals a COVID-19 scare right in the heart of Gauteng. We have to ask how many more tourists from high-risk countries are in SA right now? @XoliMngambi and @janedutton will bring you more on  #SAMorning Courtesy #DStv403 https://t.co/AVp25lwTwv
